name: CXCallDirectoryManager.EnabledStatus
desc: The enabled status of a Call Directory app extension, as reported by the getEnabledStatusForExtension(withIdentifier:completionHandler:) method.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: Indicates that the enabled status for the extension is unknown.

items.name: case disabled
items.desc: Indicates that the extension is disabled.

items.name: case enabled
items.desc: Indicates that the extension is enabled.
